igente de Moda】Este smartwatch mujer cuenta con un bisel metálico dorado y una pantalla táctil de alta definición y gran sensibilidad de 1,85 pulgadas, lo que le confiere un diseño elegante y con estilo. El smartwatch viene con dos correas (1 correa metálica + 1 correa de silicona), que se adaptan fácilmente al trabajo, el deporte y diversas ocasiones. Además, hay más de 200 estilos de esferas disponibles, con soporte para esferas personalizadas con fotos, lo que le permite personalizar su reloj único. 【24/7 Health Monitoring】The smartwatch women incorporates the latest touchscreen chip, a high-sensitivity G-sensor and PPG heart rate sensor to accurately monitor heart rate,blood pressure and sleep patterns. The sleep tracker activates automatically overnight, providing comprehensive sleep quality analysis (deep sleep, light sleep and wakefulness). The android smart watch also features stress detection and female menstrual cycle tracking, thoughtfully safeguarding your wellbeing. 【Wide Compatibility, Ideal Gift Choice】This digital watch womens is compatible with iOS 9.0 and Android 7.0 or above. This smart watches for women combines elegant design with practical functionality, available in multiple colour options. It makes the perfect gift for birthdays, holidays or everyday occasions. Whether for fitness, health or everyday convenience, it serves as a versatile choice for ladies, teenagers and seniors alike. 🛒 Aquí!!! Check the price of this item in other countries: 🇬🇧 United Kingdom | 🇺🇸 USA | 🇩🇪 Germany | 🇪🇸 Spain | 🇫🇷 France | 🇮🇹 Italia | 🇦🇪 Arab Emirates | 🇨🇦 Canada | 🇧🇪 Belgium | 🇳🇱 Neederlands | 🇵🇱 Poland | 🇸🇪 Sweden | ","id":410,"tag":"Electrónica ; Smartwatches ; Tecnología para vestir ; cascho ; iphone ; 🇪🇸","title":"CASCHO - Reloj Inteligente Mujer con Llamadas y Voz de Al Whatsapp Notificaciones 1.85\" Smartwatch Mujer con SpO2/Pulsómetro/Monitor de Sueño 120+ Modos Deportes IP68 Regalo para iPhone Android Dual Straps","url":"https://apple.tole.es/b0g2h9w